| Element   | Font  | Weight   | Size          |
| Button    | Inter | SemiBold    | 20 px / 16 px |
| Hyperlink | Inter | SemiBold | 20 px / 15 px |

Sale Price: 29 px, Bold (#C53122)
Normal Price: 18 px, Regular (Font Color)

| Role              | Hex       | Description                      |

 **Primary**        "#401713"  Deep brown, key brand tone       
| **Secondary**     | "#A65E4E" | Accent tone for highlights       |
| **Background**    | "#F2E0D0" | Main page background             |
| **Font Colour**   | "#0C0C20" | Default text color               |
| **Accent 1**      | "#735149" | Secondary shade                  |
| **Accent 2**      | "#BFA095" | Supporting tone                  |
| **Error / Alert** | "#C53122" | Error state, critical highlights |


| Context | Padding | Font           | Weight | Notes                        |
| Desktop | 15 px   | Inter SemiBold | 16 px  | FAQ, Contact, Privacy Policy |
| Mobile  | 7 px    | Inter SemiBold | 16 px  | Same links, smaller padding  |


Buttons
Primary Buttons

States: Normal / Hover / Active (background toggles between #F2E0D0 and #401713)
Border Radius: 8 px
Desktop Height: 64 px
Mobile Height: 54 px
Max Width: 462 px (desktop)
Font: Inter Light 20 px

Carousel Buttons (Desktop Only)

Heights: Desktop 49 px / Mobile 54 px
Width: max 209 px
Same color and typography system as primary buttons.
Login / Register / Payment Buttons
Follows same sizing and typography as Primary buttons.
Background alternates between light (#F2E0D0) and dark (#401713) depending on hover or focus.


Form Fields
Border: 2 px solid
Border Radius: 8 px
Inner Shadow: Subtle for depth
Desktop Height: 48 px
Mobile Height: 40 px

| State                 | Example                                       | Color                     |

| Default (Placeholder) | “placeholder”                                 | "#0C0C20" at 20% opacity |
| Focus                 | Active border                                 | "#401713"                 |
| Error                 | Field Required text                           | "#C53122"                 |
| Placeholder Text      | Padding Left 10 px / Top 14 px / Bottom 15 px | "#0C0C20" at 60% opacity |
